---
globs: apps/chrome-extensions/**/src/tests/**,apps/chrome-extensions/**/src/**
alwaysApply: false
description: Playwright/E2E expectations for Chrome extensions
---
## Use existing targets & tags
- Smoke: `pnpm nx run pmhnp-administration-summerysky:e2e -- --grep @smoke`
- Recipe slices: use `pnpm nx run pmhnp-administration-summerysky:e2e -- --grep "@recipes"` and extend existing tags.
- Side panel slice: `pnpm nx run pmhnp-administration-summerysky:e2e -- --grep @sidepanel`

## Authoring rules
- Tests must **load the unpacked extension** and **exercise the exact waits** used by content scripts (spy on logs if needed).
- Prefer **route-anchored** assertions over hard sleeps: `expect(page.url()).toMatch(/contacts\/\d+/)` **before** waiting for `[data-test-id="fieldSectionWrapperShowAll"]`.
